Kezieh  Ibe (born 6 December 1982) is an English footballer who plays for Enfield Town as a striker.
He has previously played for Yeovil Town in the Football League, and several non-League clubs including Ebbsfleet United, Farnborough and twice for Chelmsford City.His most recent transfer was from Egham Town of the Isthmian League South Central Division to Enfield Town of the Premier Division, in January 2019.
